'''Pleiades'''

#{{greekmyth}}: The "seven sisters", companions of [[Artemis]] and daughters of the [[Titan]] [[Atlas]] and the sea-[[nymph]] [[Pleione]].
#{{astronomy}}: An [[open cluster]] of hot blue [[star]]s in the [[constellation]] [[Taurus]], and the most easily visible such cluster from [[Earth]].

